CAD Models

The designs for the prototype system were developed using Autodesk Fusion 360. The core models are linked below, where download buttons can be found in the upper right of the linked site. From these links, downloads are available in the following file formats:
  • Fusion 360 Archive
  • Inventor 2021
  • IGES
  • SAT
  • SMT
  • STEP
  • DWG
  • IGES
  • DXF
  • STL
  • FBX
  • SketchUp
  • OBJ
